OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thu 2 Apr to Sat 11 AprFA
OL,6,Fbroad northwest to southeast split is
OL,7,Fexpected across the UK during this
OL,8,Fperiod. The northwest is likely to be
OL,9,Fmore unsettled with low pressure
OL,10,Fsystems moving in at times, bringing
OL,11,Fshowers or longer spells of rain.
OL,12,FStrong winds are also possible,
OL,13,Fparticularly along coasts. In the
OL,14,Fsoutheast, high pressure will have
OL,15,Fgreater influence, with more settled,
OL,16,Fdrier weather as a result.
OL,17,FTemperatures overall are likely to be
OL,18,Fnear to or slightly above normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
